FW HelloPST Do you know this guy Original Message From Sidney Jacobson Sent Saturday December PM To Jeff Young Jeff Hunter Mike Hormell Cc NishiokaYDardenvirginiaedu Subject FW Hello JeffJeff Mimi who used to be our marketing rep before returning to Grad school forwarded me the resume of a classmate and friend of hers I reviewed his resume and think he would be a great fit a Caleblight He brings physical structuring IT and energy business process experience in the energy industry with him He also wants to relocate to Houston It is clear he knows what marktomarket VaR and derivatives are Although we arent hiring now I assume he will not be available until graduation anyhow I think we should give him an interview to see if he is a good fit Jeff Young you retaking the lead on new hires now correct Sid Original Message From Nishioka Yuzuka Mimi mailtoNishiokaYDardenvirginiaedu Sent Saturday December PM To Sidney Jacobson Subject FW Hello Sidney I spoke with my friend who is interested in PA His name is Raiford Smith and he is looking for positions specifically in Houston In addition he seems to have very relevant experience for the ESRM practice see excerpt of his background in email below When I forwarded your email to him his response was that he is interested in ESRM and he has a lot of experience in industry with derivatives and IT Would you be available to talk with him Attached for your reference is his resume Thanks Sidney Mimi resumeraiford sydoc
